@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Cookie Policy";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Learn how Meet Amalfi Coasts uses cookies to improve your browsing experience and website functionality.";
}

<section class="py-5 legal-page">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">

        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
            <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">
                Last updated: July 21, 2026
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>1. What Are Cookies</h2>

            <p>
                Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website.
                They help websites function properly, improve user experience and, where applicable,
                collect information about how visitors use the website.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>

            <p>
                Meet Amalfi Coast may use cookies to ensure the correct functioning of the website,
                remember user preferences, improve website performance and analyze browsing activity.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

            <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
            <p>
                These cookies are necessary for the website to work correctly and cannot be disabled
                through our cookie banner. They are usually set in response to actions such as page
                navigation, form submissions or privacy preference settings.
            </p>

            <h3>Analytics Cookies</h3>
            <p>
                With your consent, we may use Google Analytics to collect aggregated and anonymous
                information about how visitors use the website. This helps us improve the performance,
                usability and content of our services.
            </p>

            <h3>Third-Party Cookies</h3>
            <p>
                This website may use third-party services including Stripe for secure online payments,
                Google Analytics for website analytics and Google Ads for advertising and conversion
                measurement. These providers may use cookies or similar technologies in accordance with
                their own privacy and cookie policies.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>4. Payment and Booking Services</h2>
            <p>
                Online payments are securely processed through Stripe, which may use cookies or similar
                technologies necessary to complete transactions securely.
            </p>

            <p>
                Booking information may also be synchronized with Google Calendar for internal scheduling
                purposes. Google Calendar is used solely to organize appointments and does not install
                cookies on visitors' devices through this website.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>5. Cookie Categories</h2>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Essential Cookies</strong> - Required for the website to function correctly.</li>

                <li><strong>Analytics Cookies</strong> - Used only with your consent to analyze website usage through Google Analytics.</li>

                <li><strong>Marketing Cookies</strong> - Used only with your consent to measure advertising campaigns and conversions through Google Ads.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>


        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>6. Managing Cookie Preferences</h2>

            <p>
                When you first visit the website, you can choose whether to accept or reject
                non-essential cookies through the cookie banner.
            </p>

            <p>
                Your preferences can be changed at any time by reopening the cookie settings,
                where available, or by modifying your browser settings.
            </p>
        </div>



        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>7. Disabling Cookies from Your Browser</h2>

            <p>
                Most browsers allow you to manage, block or delete cookies through their settings.
                Please note that disabling essential cookies may affect the proper functioning of
                some parts of the website.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <h2>8. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>

            <p>
                We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in technology,
                legal requirements or the services offered through the website.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h2>9. Contact</h2>

            <p>
                If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact us using the contact details provided on this website.
            </p>
        </div>

            </div>
        </section>